column5: Went fishing. Caught some fish. Went home. Here's pics.        The end.
Long drive, short report  It was a short, but good outing. Why didn't you mention anything about catching a pike? haha.  That walleye you're holding is a beast!
No pics, no proof, no pike.
How did the sled run chad?

Forward good...reverse is grindy. I'm happy with the sled but I'm worried about the reverse function in the chaincase. I gotta get that looked at soon.  The snow banks are tiny and fluffy right now, it's tough to load the sled back into the truck.
I will give you credit for a pike without the picture. Nice trip for sure.   Art
Great outing guys. Come on Chad…put some effort in…just lift the sled back on the truck (says the man with the gimpy elbow)
Those are some nice bars of gold guys.
